&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Why Visit Copenhagen?
 &lt;div id="why-visit-copenhagen" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#why-visit-copenhagen" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Copenhagen, the capital of &lt;a href="https://visafree.techpawz.com/posts/denmark-visa-free/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Denmark&lt;/a&gt;, is a vibrant city that effortlessly blends rich history with modern innovation. As you stroll through its picturesque streets, you&amp;rsquo;ll find a unique charm in the colorful Nyhavn harbor, the iconic Little Mermaid statue, and the lush gardens of Tivoli. The city is renowned for its commitment to sustainability, cycling culture, and progressive lifestyle, making it a haven for eco-conscious travelers. With its blend of medieval architecture and cutting-edge design, Copenhagen has something to offer every type of traveler.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>